                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12669527" author="fmeschbe" created="Mon, 2 Feb 2009 08:29:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Implemented in Rev 739941: All remote shell connections are registered when started and unregistered when terminated. When the remote shell bundle is stopped, all remote shell connections still registered are closed down to ensure the bundle is properly stopped and can be garbage collected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
